HEADWORD: hibernating
<hw>hibernating</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>in a state of suspended
animation; -- of animals that sleep most of the winter.</def>
<mark>[prenominal]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> dormant, torpid.</syn>⟦br⟧
